timelineItems.name: Mandy Stark
timelineItems.text: So excited for this game. We're going to BEAT Vancouver. #SKCvVAN #SportingKC

timelineItems.name: NEWS 1130 Sports
timelineItems.text: Kekuta Manneh has the Whitecaps on the board in the 8th minute - lead Sporting Kansas City 1-nil. #VWFC

timelineItems.name: Eighty Six Forever
timelineItems.text: I know there's still 80-odd minutes to go but hot damn it was nice to see my earlier #SKC taunting not backfire. Thank you, Kekuta. #VWFC

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 11' Manneh given space to shoot from 25 yards out and he hammers it well over the crossbar. #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: Sporting Kansas City
timelineItems.text: #SportingKC #SKC #KCCauldron #mls Sporting Kansas City vs. Vancouver Whitecaps Match Thread http://t.co/L0s54h24nx

timelineItems.name: Joseph Macht
timelineItems.text: Home in time to watch #SKC & #Chiefs with daddy! http://t.co/vSJ37o1IKf

timelineItems.name: Vancouver Whitecaps
timelineItems.text: 9' Scooter forces the turnover, brings it him himself & slots it home with his left foot. Nice poise for a 20 year old. #VWFC #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.desc: Attempt saved. Paulo Nagamura (Sporting Kansas City) left footed shot from a difficult angle on the left is saved in the center of the goal.
timelineItems.title: SAVE: David Ousted saves one-on-one chance from Nagamura

timelineItems.name: Will GT
timelineItems.text: OUSTED! #VWFC

timelineItems.name: The Blue Testament
timelineItems.text: Be still my heart, that pass by Feilhaber. Dwyer can’t get a good hold of it in the box but still, my goodness what a pass. #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: Eighty Six Forever
timelineItems.text: Ousted made that look easy. You'd have put money on Dwyer to score there. #SKC aren't going down without a fight. #SKCvVAN #VWFC

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 17' Sublime ball over the top from Feilhaber to Nagamura, whose left-footed shot is saved! Terrific chance carved out by the hosts! #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.desc: The Vancouver Whitecaps face off against Sporting Kansas City in this Western Conference showdown.
timelineItems.title: KICKOFF: Sporting Kansas City vs. Vancouver Whitecaps | August 15, 2015

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 19' Thunderous punt downfield from Melia to Nemeth, who does very well to bring it down and win SKC a throw-in. #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: Eighty Six Forever
timelineItems.text: The "shots" clap again? Come on, try something else, home crowd. Variety is the spice of life - and winning teams. #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.desc: Attempt blocked. Connor Hallisey (Sporting Kansas City) left footed shot from the centre of the box is blocked. Assisted by Benny Feilhaber.
timelineItems.title: CHANCE: Crazy sequence ends with Hallisey shot deflecting out

timelineItems.desc: The Vancouver Whitecaps face off against Sporting Kansas City in this Western Conference showdown
timelineItems.title: HIGHLIGHTS: Sporting Kansas City vs. Vancouver Whitecaps | August 15, 2015

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 21' WHAT. A. CHANCE!!! Stunning 1-2 between Nemeth & Dwyer before a shot falls to Hallisey, and it's blocked off the line! #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: Vancouver Whitecaps
timelineItems.text: 20' Crazy action in the WFC box. First Ousted with the save and then Harvey comes up big. #VWFC #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: Padraig MUFC
timelineItems.text: Picture of David Ousted's goal #VWFC @WhitecapsFC http://t.co/x7zzf957L1

timelineItems.name: Eighty Six Forever
timelineItems.text: Harvey was/is amazing there but you have to feel for Adekugbe. How does Sam crack the lineup with Harvey in the form of his life? #VWFC

timelineItems.name: Alex Seder
timelineItems.text: What game is Medranda playing? #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: Kasey Hunter
timelineItems.text: Anyone in Kansas. Please find the dude with the trumpet and take a hammer to said trumpet. #SKCvVAN #MLS

timelineItems.name: Eighty Six Forever
timelineItems.text: Far too easily given up there by Techera. Play first, complain after. #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: John Knight
timelineItems.text: Jordan Harvey has developed into a premier left back, a la Luke Shaw! Great to see! #VWFC

timelineItems.name: Eighty Six Forever
timelineItems.text: Wait, there are actually people watching #DALvLA instead of #SKCvVAN? You poor, poor fools. #VWFC

timelineItems.name: Kasey Hunter
timelineItems.text: Nice buildup by SKC but Vancouver back four stand tall. Good contest between the two best teams in the west. #WhitecapsFC #SKCvVAN #MLS

timelineItems.name: Eighty Six Forever
timelineItems.text: I would not be shocked at all if this match ends up being a preview of the Western Conference semi-final. Or, heck, the final. #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: Andy Edwards
timelineItems.text: #SportingKC still not totally awake/in this game. #VWFC sitting much deeper now, just soaking up pressure very well/easily. #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: Eighty Six Forever
timelineItems.text: I disagree that Nico is "keeping Morales out" of this XI. Pedro is sorely needed to balance the other XI. Best of both worlds. #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 39' Another cross from Dia is blocked out for a corner. Feilhaber's service is successfully defended by Vancouver. #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: Eighty Six Forever
timelineItems.text: 35' - shades of a #SKC handball there to break up a through-ball to Rivero. Was it? #InstantReplay #VWFC #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.desc: Goal!  Sporting Kansas City 0, Vancouver Whitecaps FC 2. Kekuta Manneh (Vancouver Whitecaps FC) header from the center of the box
timelineItems.title: GOAL: Kekuta Manneh grabs a brace to double Vancouver's lead

timelineItems.name: Andy Edwards
timelineItems.text: Note to Soni Mustivar: Kekuta Manneh is plenty fast enough to jump your passing lanes. All of them. #SportingKC #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: Eighty Six Forever
timelineItems.text: In a clash of high press vs. high press, the speedier midfield wins. See also: Manneh, Kekuta and Laba, Matias. #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: Simon Fudge
timelineItems.text: G41' - Another turnover, another @WhitecapsFC goal! Beitashour given too much time to pick out Manneh for his 2nd of the game! #SKCvVAN #MLS

timelineItems.name: GlassCity
timelineItems.text: HOT DAMN!!! What a ball from Beitashour and a great headed finish by Manneh. #VWFC

timelineItems.name: MyScores.ca
timelineItems.text: Kekuta Manneh with 2 goals to have #VWFC up at half http://t.co/O3FyqKEK8N

timelineItems.name: Vancouver Whitecaps
timelineItems.text: Keep them coming Kekuta! Here's his 2nd of the match: http://t.co/8TLH12gxyn #VWFC #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: Eighty Six Forever
timelineItems.text: Mmm, a halftime highlights pack consisting of the wailing and gnashing of #TFC teeth? I'll allow it. (Still, where's my Manneh?!) #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: Challengers Podcast
timelineItems.text: #SKC has had 70% possession, 83% passing accuracy, but two HUGE turnovers and #VWFC with a 75% shooting pct. is our difference. #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: Eighty Six Forever
timelineItems.text: I have to assume part of the #VWFC blind-spot phenomenon in USA is b/c we're Canadian. It'd be like Swansea challenging for EPL title.

timelineItems.name: Vancouver Whitecaps
timelineItems.text: At the half, it's 2-0 for the good guys at Sporting Park. Manneh with Brace. #VWFC #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: Peter Galindo
timelineItems.text: Octavio Rivero is so strong, but that's a great save by Tim Melia. #SKC #VWFC

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 4' Ousted gets his fist to Feilhaber's in-swinger and Nagamura's 22-yard volley on the rebound sails high and wide. #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.desc: Attempt saved. Octavio Rivero (Vancouver Whitecaps FC) right footed shot from the center of the box is saved in the center of the goal.
timelineItems.title: SAVE: Tim Melia saves one-on-one chance from Rivero

timelineItems.name: GlassCity
timelineItems.text: Manneh isn't putting the work in defensively, keeps hanging Harvey out to dry. #VWFC

timelineItems.desc: Goal!  Sporting Kansas City 1, Vancouver Whitecaps FC 2. Kevin Ellis (Sporting Kansas City) header from very close range
timelineItems.title: GOAL: Kevin Ellis pulls a goal back for Sporting KC

timelineItems.name: Eighty Six Forever
timelineItems.text: 53' - I don't suppose there's a chance the #SKC goal was offside? #InstantReplay #VWFC #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: Eighty Six Forever
timelineItems.text: On the plus side, surely that goal will galvanize the #VWFC into tightening up. Like I said, #SKC are always dangerous. #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: Bryan Everson
timelineItems.text: Suddenly inspired, Ellis with a goal off the corner and its a game. Vancouver were giving a little too much prior to the set piece #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: Joe Tansey
timelineItems.text: How good has Kevin Ellis been recently? Arguably best CB on form in MLS right now. #SportingKC #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: 53' Feilhaber's corner wasn't cleared and Mustivar's looping header was nodded home at the far post by @Kev_Ellis4! 1-2 #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday
timelineItems.text: That's the 3rd goal of the year for homegrown defender @Kev_Ellis4, while @billydougie earns his first @MLS assist. #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.desc: Attempt saved. Octavio Rivero (Vancouver Whitecaps FC) right footed shot from the center of the box is saved in the center of the goal.
timelineItems.title: SAVE: Tim Melia runs out to make a huge save

timelineItems.name: Eighty Six Forever
timelineItems.text: Wowwwwwwwww Manneh. That was something else. Did everything right. Melia came up massive. #SKCvVAN #VWFC

timelineItems.name: Johnnie Monster
timelineItems.text: When Ousted's shutout slips away #VWFC supporters be like: http://t.co/PTIEHjiWap

timelineItems.name: Jason Weaver
timelineItems.text: Great save from Melia. Is that kind of speed from Manneh legal? #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: Joe Tansey
timelineItems.text: Manneh has to be selfish there. Could be 3-1 if he keeps it. #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.name: Vancouver Whitecaps
timelineItems.text: 59' Sub: Rosales on for Techera. #VWFC #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.text: Rosales back fit and on for Techera on the hour mark... #SKCvVAN #MLS

timelineItems.name: Aaron Campbell
timelineItems.text: How big of an issue would Riveros lack of goals be if the Whitecaps weren't getting results? Sooner or later he needs to score. #VWFC

timelineItems.name: SKC Gameday

timelineItems.name: Woosang Lee
timelineItems.text: Rivero missing some good chances. He can't seem to score unless it's a PK...& he's the striker. #VWFC

timelineItems.title: SAVE: Tim Melia makes another one-on-one save

timelineItems.name: Eighty Six Forever
timelineItems.text: Oh, good! It's not just Rivero. Manneh now finding Melia a tough nut to crack. That was far too easy, though... #SKCvVAN

timelineItems.text: Bringing Darren Mattocks off the bench after Manneh terrorized #SportingKC for 74 minutes is just not fair. #SKCvVAN
